  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2025-10-17 18:26</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p>基础语言模型MobileLLM-Pro，Markdown模型Nanonets-OCR2，多模态模型Home-cooked Mistral Small Omni，聊天界面项目chat-ui，文档AI引擎PaddleOCR，优化方法EPO</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=966e775e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhEqLbibUDr2eLMwiajibxK3CibEWsUSfVaCW6ISWCNLeQDCG4p34xibO9dQjQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MobileLLM-Pro</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"870\" data-imgfileid=\"100016203\" data-ratio=\"0.8269961977186312\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1052\" data-width=\"1052\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5e714f46&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhEeDljFWkcRoOVxXQ39ibPxFok4sAgIZI37Kia5ZFI59YAj0UUp0DczgkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MobileLLM-Pro 是 MobileLLM 系列中的一个基础语言模型，拥有 10 亿参数，专为在移动设备上高效执行各种通用语言建模任务而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目开源了两个模型变体：一个预训练的基础模型和一个指令微调版本。MobileLLM-Pro 在工具调用、问答、重写和摘要等任务上表现出色，支持长达 128k 的上下文窗口，适用于文档摘要和信息检索等应用。模型通过量化技术实现了高效的设备端推理，提供了接近无损的 int4 量化检查点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mobilellm-pro2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mobilellm-pro2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Nanonets-OCR2-3B</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"644\" data-imgfileid=\"100016199\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b274b29c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhENEjUgnibQvloJDVdZToyxkxTy86cebLmAJdRdia00B7ek9avOyNfy4uA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Nanonets-OCR2-3B 是一款先进的图像到 Markdown OCR 模型，能够超越传统的文本提取。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它将文档转换为结构化的 Markdown，具备智能内容识别和语义标记功能，非常适合大型语言模型（LLMs）的下游处理。该模型能够处理复杂文档，支持多种语言，并提供视觉问答功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanonets-ocr2-3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanonets-ocr2-3b</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Home-cooked Mistral Small Omni</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"590\" data-imgfileid=\"100016200\" data-ratio=\"0.5138888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1148\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ce52bbe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhEXzvYiawjoJD3AibOhJnag0nR9W4sFV2MTllS6sugbRZZEA2kVrAvDnsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Home-Cook-Mistral-Small-Omni-24B-2507-GGUF 是一个多模态模型，通过合并具有视觉能力的 Mistral Small 2506 和具有音频能力的 Voxtral 2507 创建。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在结合这两个模型的视觉和音频能力，提供更全面的多模态处理能力。模型在 Apache 2.0 许可下发布，允许用户自由使用和修改。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/home-cooked-mistral-small-omni\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/home-cooked-mistral-small-omni</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：chat-ui</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"590\" data-imgfileid=\"100016201\" data-ratio=\"0.5111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1154\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=839e43be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhExFyZ3mAqcPWVo3keacg8sfjsvr62USSjNPbHWGyuC3EhTWnniaA6u6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★HuggingChat是一个开源的聊天界面项目，基于SvelteKit构建，专为大语言模型（LLMs）设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它为HuggingChat应用提供支持，允许用户通过OpenAI兼容的API进行交互。该项目旨在简化与AI模型的对话体验，支持多种服务集成，适用于需要自然语言处理能力的应用场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/chat-ui\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/chat-ui</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：PaddleOCR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"750\" data-imgfileid=\"100016202\" data-ratio=\"0.6472222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f21897b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhENxiakzeUj8sT3p6prn8KZCUyht5xLFqib1bcYG5sZ9d1wN723bQJPbDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★PaddleOCR是一个行业领先的、可用于生产的OCR和文档AI引擎，提供从文本提取到智能文档理解的端到端解决方案。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目支持将PDF或图像文档转换为结构化数据，适用于AI应用。PaddleOCR支持100多种语言，具有高精度和轻量级的特点，广泛应用于从独立开发者到大型企业的智能文档应用开发中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/paddleocr2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/paddleocr2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：EPO</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"406\" data-imgfileid=\"100016204\" data-ratio=\"0.3527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1150\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=411eabd3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkx8iaqEwpB6t1Ib1oMRSOVhEN3scRQnnXadUy897sFRUUMYP712WpFtsk88dbRasZy92rpicHFEibDqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EPO项目提出了一种新颖的熵正则化策略优化方法，用于通过强化学习训练大语言模型代理。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该方法通过引入熵正则化来提高训练的稳定性和泛化性能，特别适用于多轮代理环境。实验结果表明，与基线方法相比，EPO增强的方法在奖励积累和训练稳定性方面有显著提升。在ScienceWorld中，PPO+EPO的训练奖励约为基线方法的两倍，并且表现出平滑的单调轨迹；在ALFWorld中，GRPO+EPO在整个训练过程中保持稳定的上升趋势。验证性能显示，在40个训练步骤内，成功率迅速收敛到高于0.8，而基线方法即使在100个步骤后也难以超过0.4。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/epo-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/epo-2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100012181\" data-ratio=\"1.5712962962962962\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=050dd75e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzsuveu0Oib7RPoas9iaReIDLd72zAJkrNOCp7A0IRgbeicADqBSicz36BLdGh2dz1C7E5PZgibCqFNSRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"107\" data-imgfileid=\"100013546\" data-ratio=\"0.18518518518518517\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);letter-spacing: 0.578px;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73250edd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky46ibiaDkwPpOl085OGW8JMM572LKqicN8ordMGb1lKKwclv8NbFEOlFRqAojINufXDNiaERbIkUv8EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></span><span style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <p><strong style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 黑体, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2247499894\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=f759f3a8&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzkyMzcwMDIyMQ%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247499894%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D6cf940a4f4c087ffdb1398f253907aea\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "今日 AI 开源项目汇总，重点介绍了 Facebook MobileLLM-Pro 等具备超长上下文和跨任务泛化能力的移动端 LLM，以及多模态、OCR 和 LLM 代理优化等前沿技术。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "今日 AI 开源项目汇总，重点介绍了 Facebook MobileLLM-Pro 等具备超长上下文和跨任务泛化能力的移动端 LLM，以及多模态、OCR 和 LLM 代理优化等前沿技术。",
  "summary": "文章以“今日开源”的形式，汇总了 2025 年 10 月 17 日发布的六个重要的 AI 开源项目。首先介绍了 Facebook 的 MobileLLM-Pro，一个专为移动设备设计、拥有 10 亿参数的基础语言模型，其亮点在于支持 128k 的超长上下文窗口，并在工具调用、问答、重写和摘要等任务上表现出色，同时提供高效的 int4 量化检查点。接着，文章提及了 Nanonets-OCR2-3B，一个能将图像转换为结构化 Markdown 的先进 OCR 模型，适用于 LLM 的下游处理。多模态方面，Home-cooked Mistral Small Omni 通过合并视觉和音频能力，提供了更全面的多模态处理方案。此外，还包括 HuggingChat 的开源聊天界面 chat-ui，百度出品的生产级 OCR 和文档 AI 引擎 PaddleOCR，以及用于强化学习训练大语言模型代理的熵正则化策略优化方法 EPO。整篇文章旨在为 AI 开发者提供最新的开源技术动态和实用工具。",
